Thomas  Kurian 
Executive Compensation
As President, Product Development at ORACLE CORP, Thomas  Kurian  made $35,743,145 in total compensation.  Of this total $800,000 was received as a salary, $0 was received as a bonus, $15,490,400 was received in stock options, $19,440,000 was awarded as stock and $12,745 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


