Kurian Thomas, MD, MBBS is a Doctor primarily located in Chicago, IL. He has 16 years of experience. His specialties include Neurology.                      Kurian Thomas is affiliated with                            Resurrection Medical Center,                            Chicago Health Care System - West Side Div. - Jessie Brown Hospital and                            University Of Illinois Medical Center At Chicago.
